      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty car. It\u2019s been such a fantastic ride and is still in really wonderful shape! It runs smoothly, looks great, and has been well-loved during its time with me. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make its next owner very happy. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and get you behind the wheel!",
