    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3, a purist-spec example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This chassis remains exceptionally balanced, with the rear subframe reinforced for long-term structural integrity. Power is routed through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential lock, providing superb tactile feedback and traction. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings and dampers, ensuring the legendary handling characteristics of the E46 platform are preserved. Maintained with a focus on preventative mechanical care, this M3 is optimized for the driving enthusiast who values engineering precision and naturally aspirated performance.",
