      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the perfect balance of performance and meticulous upkeep. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish, showing only the minor, unavoidable stone chips consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the leather remains supple, and all interior electronics, including the infotainment and climate systems, function flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having followed a strict preventative maintenance schedule. It features a smooth-shifting transmission, a responsive engine with no leaks, and a recently replaced set of premium all-season tires. Every service record has been preserved in a comprehensive binder, which will be passed on to the new owner along with both original keys. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next chapter, offering a driving experience that is both refined and reliable.",
