      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically sorted BMW E46 M3, a quintessential driver's machine. This example features the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, which remains internally sound with a recently serviced VANOS system to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The structural integrity has been addressed with rear subframe reinforcement plates, a critical preventative measure for this chassis. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, tactile shifts, directing power through a consistent 25% lock-up limited-slip differential. Performance is further bolstered by refreshed suspension bushings and a cooling system overhaul. While the aesthetic reflects its 'good' condition status with minor road wear, the drivetrain and chassis dynamics are dialed in for immediate spirited use.",
